data.description: *~* Buyers lost financing - their loss is your gain! *~* Excellent opportunity to own this large 2 family home in an established Webster neighborhood! This fully rented property is situated on a corner lot and offers 2 sun drenched units! Both units offer an attractive floorplan with 3 good sized bedrooms, full baths, large living rooms, spacious kitchens w/ dining areas & formal dining rooms w/ built in shelving. Both units also offer convenient laundry hookups! This home provides both front and side covered porches, plenty of outdoor space with a partially fenced in backyard & off-street parking! Additional features: Large walk-up attic, gas heat w/ separate utilities, newer roof, conveniently located to schools, shopping, restaurants, and highway access! Great commuter location with a neighborhood feel! Don't miss out on this one!
